data.meta_description: William Davis was born in the year 1635 in Warrosquyoake, Virginia, United States, son of Thomas Davis and Elizabeth. He was married in the year 1665 to Sary Jarvis, they gave birth to 1 child. He died in the year 1680 in Pasquotank, North Carolina, United States. This information is part of Davis Family Tree by William H Davis III on Genealogy Online.
